commentText:
Determine the next execution time according to the given trigger context._

Next execution times are calculated based on the_{@linkplain TriggerContext#lastCompletionTime completion time} of the_previous execution_ therefore, overlapping executions won't occur.
codeText: @Override_	public Date nextExecutionTime(TriggerContext triggerContext) {_		Date date = triggerContext.lastCompletionTime()__		if (date != null) {_			Date scheduled = triggerContext.lastScheduledExecutionTime()__			if (scheduled != null && date.before(scheduled)) {_				_				_				_				date = scheduled__			}_		}_		else {_			date = new Date()__		}_		return this.sequenceGenerator.next(date)__	}
